data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2 and a half bathroom residence sits gracefully on a sprawling 1.36-acre lot, offering you the perfect blend of space, comfort, and modern living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, breakfast area, and kitchen areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, featuring a large center island that serves as a focal point, allowing for effortless meal preparation, and casual conversations. Natural light pours in through strategically placed windows, enhancing the ambiance the overall ambience.  The inclusion of ceiling fans throughout ensures a comfortable environment year-round, promoting circulation and maintaining a pleasant indoor climate. Unwind and cool off during those sunny days in the above-ground pool, where you can bask in the sun's rays or take a refreshing dip. Imagine hosting memorable summer barbecues and pool parties with friends and loved ones in this private backyard oasis. For those with a penchant for vehicles or hobbies, the spacious 3-car garage offers ample storage and workspace options, accommodating your every need. This property's generous acreage provides space for endless possibilities, whether you're an avid gardener, desire extra outdoor space, or simply crave the tranquility of wide-open spaces. Come take a look at this home today, it will not disappoint! Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
